#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije i Savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Go is more about surrounding territory (empty space) than capturing your "
#| "opponent's pieces."
msgid ""
"<literal>Go</literal> is more about surrounding territory (empty space) than "
"capturing your opponent's pieces."
msgstr ""
"Go je više o okolnom području (praznom prostoru) nego hvatanje komada vašeg "
"protivnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Territory is easiest to surround near the corners (on two sides) then near "
"the edges (on three sides) and lastly in the center."
msgstr ""
"Teritoriu je najlakše okružuti u blizini uglova (na dvije strane), a zatim u "
"blizini rubova (na tri strane) i na kraju u centru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the start of the game, space your pieces out. Only fill in your fence-"
"lines when your opponent starts to intrude"
msgstr ""
"Na početku igre, izbacite vaše komade napolje . Samo ispunite vaše ogradne "
"linije kada vaš protivnik počne da napada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Do not play unsupported stones right next to your opponent's stones when "
#| "attacking. They will tend to get swallowed and GnuGo is very good at "
#| "that. It is often better to attack indirectly."
msgid ""
"Do not play unsupported stones right next to your opponent's stones when "
"attacking. They will tend to get swallowed and &gnugo; is very good at that. "
"It is often better to attack indirectly."
msgstr ""
"Ne igraj nepodržane kamenje tik do kamenja vašeg protivnika kada napada. Oni "
"će nastojati da se proguta i GnuGo je vrlo dobar u tome. Često je bolje da "
"napadnete indirektno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To avoid capture, a group of stones must have two <quote>eyes</quote> or be "
"able to make them if attacked. <quote>Eyes</quote> are disconnected spaces. "
"Think of a doughnut with two holes. Your opponent can surround the outside, "
"but cannot fill both holes at once."
msgstr ""
"Da bi izbjegli zarobljavanje, grupa kamenja mora imati dva  <quote>oči</"
"quote> ili ih biti u stanju napraviti ako su napadnuti. <quote>Oči</quote> "
"su isključen prostori. Razmislite o krofni sa dvije rupe. Vaš protivnik može "
"okružiti izvana, ali ne može da popuni obje rupe odjednom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the 19x19 board there are typically several territories being created, "
"attacked or defended. You have to fight several battles simultaneously. The "
"strategy involves evaluating the strengths and weaknesses in various areas "
"and allocating your moves between them. Is it better to attack there or "
"defend here?"
msgstr ""
"Na ploči 19x19 postoji obično nekoliko područja koja se kreiraju, napadačka "
"ili branjena. Morate boriti nekoliko borbi istovremeno. Strategija uključuje "
"vrijednovanje prednosti i slabosti u različitim područjima i dodjelu svojih "
"poteza između njih. Da li je bolje da napadaju tamo ili da brane ovdje?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
