#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The most important aspect here is the Go engine backend conﬁguration. "
#| "&kappname; needs a valid backend to function properly. As you can see in "
#| "the screenshot below, it used GnuGo by default. The little light next to "
